name: EfficientNet
description: Constructs a EfficientNet architecture from “EfficientNet: Rethinking Model Scaling for Convolutional Neural Networks”.

properties._description:
model_name (string): Specific variant model of the EfficientNet model class, containing efficientnet_b0, efficientnet_b1... 
pretrained (bool): If True, returns a model pre-trained on ImageNet
progress (bool): If True, displays a progress bar of the download to stderr
num_classes (int): Number of categories
